get their information about
democracy from local television

00:26:49.620 --> 00:26:50.880
news.

00:26:50.880 --> 00:26:54.180
Now, I'm not going to ask you
to watch your local television

00:26:54.180 --> 00:26:55.090
news.

00:26:55.090 --> 00:26:58.570
That would be an unreasonable
