00:50:07.900 --> 00:50:10.050
By 2010, it was down to 20%.

00:50:10.050 --> 00:50:11.325
Today it's under 10%.

00:50:11.325 --> 00:50:13.640
And it's approaching
0% like a parabola.

00:50:13.640 --> 00:50:15.490
So there's not a
commercial market left,

00:50:15.490 --> 00:50:17.740
which is why Bezos got
it for such little money.

00:50:17.740 --> 00:50:20.100
In our view, to sum
up really quickly,

00:50:20.100 --> 00:50:23.250
this is a fundamental political
issue for this country.

00:50:23.250 --> 00:50:25.700
