incredible press system.

00:50:52.402 --> 00:50:53.860
And what we find
in other countries

00:50:53.860 --> 00:50:56.720
is enlightened policies in
places like Germany, Denmark,

00:50:56.720 --> 00:51:00.790
Norway, and Sweden that spawn
an independent, uncensored free

00:51:00.790 --> 00:51:04.544
press and also supports diverse
newspapers in communities too.

00:51:04.544 --> 00:51:06.460
I'm not saying we should
